summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of 34th Avenue Northwest from West 62nd Street to West 68th, et all in the City of Seattle by grading, etc., under Ordinance No. 25361, creating Local Improvement District No. 2416 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
